{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"927e6ca3ac","title":"对肖华关于派干部深入部队检查工作的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92c9413c78","index":0,"year":1953,"month":3,"day":5,"articleId":"927e6ca3ac"}],"tags":[{"id":"06af9ed14a","name":"肖华","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"d692e524cf","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"肖华，当时任人民革命军事委员会总政治部副主任。"},{"id":"4095b52d13","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指肖华1953年3月5日关于派干部深入部队检查工作问题给毛泽东、彭德怀的报告。报告中说，为了贯彻中央反对官像主义的指示，拟采用分批派道干部深入部队检查工作的办法，以推进全军开展这一运动。总政治部第一期检查工作的人员共分五组，各组检查工作时间为一个月至一个半月。检查重点为各军区的主力部队及文化教育工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"b00a68663f","type":"title","text":"对肖华关于派干部深人部队检香工作的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"},{"id":"d692e524cf","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"},{"id":"4095b52d13","type":"paragraph","text":"分组下去检查很好。惟每组每次检查时间一个月至一个半月时简似太长，以半月至二十天回来报告为适宜，过几个月再去检查一次。如以一个半月时间而论，可分三次去，每次半个月尽够了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"},{"id":"4c09a2548f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"},{"id":"f24135a111","type":"paragraph","text":"三月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"},{"id":"8af62a271c","type":"paragraph","text":"坐飞机、火车、汽车，半个月可看看许多地方","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac"}],"page":{"id":"04d881e847","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"927e6ca3ac","start":39,"end":39}}}},"__N_SSG":true}